text: Dark City is a 1998 American Australian science fiction movie directed by Alex Proyas and starring Rufus Sewell, William Hurt, Kiefer Sutherland, Jennifer Connelly, Richard O'Brien, Ian Richardson. It was distributed by New Line Cinema and was a box office bomb. == Other websites == * * * Category:1998 science fiction movies Category:American science fiction movies Category:Australian science fiction movies Category:Movies directed by Alex Proyas
